filetype: PE32 executable (GUI) Intel 80386, for MS Windows

metadata.Comments: MP3 player that includes an MP3-to-WAV decoder as well as a WAV-to-MP3 decoder. Other features include scrolling ID3 tag support, a VU meter, volume control, and MPEG info displays.The encoder and decoder have list support for batch encoding and decoding. Also, there is now an Update Playlist feature, lower CPU usage, and skin support is available to change the interface's look and feel. The latest version even supports full movie playback in formats such as DiVx, AVI, MPEG, VCD, and several other popular formats.
